Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.58,0:01:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z čeho budeme psát ten test?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Však nám to včera říkal, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jo, ale víš jak!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nazdar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hele, máš po škole čas?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:01:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jasně.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chci se někam podívat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jo a kam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jako obyčejně.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jako obyčejně?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak jo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vážně? Prima.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jasně, jdu s tebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak dík.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V pohodě.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nazdar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:36.76,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.55\fad(0,979)}Květy zla
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:36.76,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.55\fad(0,979)}Epizoda první
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:41.32,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}We really shouldn't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:41.32,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}dakedo shicha ikenai no desu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:45.45,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}So accept your wounds, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:45.45,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}dakara kizutsuite shimae
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:49.16,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}An angel flies through heaps of trash
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:49.16,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}garakuta ni tenshi ga tobu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:53.34,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}I'm a piece of shit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:53.34,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}kusorashiki no boku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:59.22,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}I hate flower arrangement when it misses the mark
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:59.22,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}oshii kadou ga kiraida
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}I keep adding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.88,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}kitto boku wa machigai to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:07.16,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}to my sins and mistakes day in, day out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:07.16,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}tsumi wo kasaneteku no desu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:15.22,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}Rather than the beginning or end of a story, I'd like to see the flower bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:15.22,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}owari to hajimari yori mo sakimi no ga ne mitakute
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:19.13,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}I can't endure it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:19.13,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}tamaranai no desu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:34.16,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}Bloom, flower, and open the sprouts of sin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:34.16,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}sake yo hana hana tsumi no me wo dashite
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:38.80,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}Bloom, flower, and see your buds lorded over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:38.80,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}sake yo hana hana shihai sareteku tsubomi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:46.41,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}I'm chasing a hope that will ruin me like flowers in fall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:46.41,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}harahara sasetewa kareru kibou oikateteshimau
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:51.08,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}I won't let you be alone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:51.08,OP top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.45\fad(200,200)}hitori ni sasenai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A on se pak z ničeho nic naštval.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hele, tak naštvaný jsem nebyl. Že ne, Kojimo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Co já vím.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasugo, proč si s náma aspoň něco nezahraješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, ne že bych nechtěl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prostě mi to moc nejde.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No tak, nehraj to na nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nech mě!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak vážení, všichni sednout!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamado, stačilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pohyb, pohyb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Studuji střední školu v Ba... Ba... Ba-Bangkoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chce to trénovat, pane Kojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Další, slečna Saeki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Náš Novoroční festival se koná 13., 14., a 15. dubna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nazývá se Songkran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Během festivalu se lidé...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Připravit, hrajem...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tady!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jéééé!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stehna nemůžou být stehna, pokud nejsou aspoň trochu macatá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne? A co teda jsou?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobře, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako, to bylo skvělý!
