Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:22.12,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody had ever seen it before, and it seemed to bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:22.12,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,daremo mita koto nai hana ga saiteita you da
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:28.44,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The flower, the flower bloomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:28.44,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,hana ga hana ga saita yo
