Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:32.49,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,hana ga hana ga saita yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:39.06,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,None had seen it before, and it seemed to bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:39.06,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,mita koto nai hana ga saiteita yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:39.06,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}"There's no flower."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:39.06,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}hana nado nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:46.80,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,"There shouldn't be a flower."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:46.80,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,sore wa aru hazu mo nai to omottetara shitara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:49.91,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Some were convinced it was so.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:49.91,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,sou shitara shitara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:54.64,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But they were wrong, and it was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:54.64,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,hanagagaga aru da yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:22:56.98,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,None had ever seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:22:56.98,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,daremo mita koto nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:22:59.39,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be harsh to listen to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.98,0:22:59.39,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,neiro hazu mo nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:03.75,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,A flower bloomed that should not have.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:03.75,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,saku hazu mo nai hana ga saiteta shi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:06.39,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is, yes, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:06.39,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,soko ni yahari soko nite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:10.43,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:10.43,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,shikari soko ni soko ni aru da yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:11.74,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}The flower bloomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:11.74,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}hana ga saita yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.79,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The flower, the flower bloomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.79,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,hana ga hana ga saita yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.79,0:23:16.83,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It was terribly afraid of the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.79,0:23:16.83,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,hidoku kaze ni obieta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:22.18,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody had ever seen it before, and it bloomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:22.18,ED 2,,0000,0000,0000,,daremo mita koto nai hana ga saiteita yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Přestaň, sakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kasugo, pořád tu knihu čteš dokola.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jmenuje se "Květy zla".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.37,0:23:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zní to jako něco šíleně úchylného.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...neexistuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasuga...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Viděl jsem to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Už nemůžu dál.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.78,0:23:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Úchvatné.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak či tak to bude obtížné.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.99,0:23:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Na oplátku se mnou uzavři smlouvu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.96,0:23:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vykvetl květ.